    instruction = "Prepare maps and consumables before leaving Jeuno for the Magicite route.",
    map_grid = "",
    notes = {"Buy Davoi, Castle Oztroja, Beadeaux, and Qulun Dome maps if missing; city map vendors sell the dungeon maps for 3,000 Gil.", "Bring Silent Oil and Prism Powder for Castle Oztroja, Echo Drops for Beadeaux if you cast magic, and a Warp option for returning to Jeuno.", "Use Invisible around Davoi and Castle Oztroja, Sneak in Beadeaux, and remove Invisible before interacting with doors or Magicite.", "The four preliminary key items can be obtained in any order; if you already have them from another nation, skip to the Magicite steps."},
