    instruction = "Enter Spire of Vahzl at (F-8), rest, then click the Web of Recollections and choose Desires of Emptiness. Buffs wear on entry, so buff inside. Fight Procreator, Cumulator, and Agonizer; the next boss joins when the current one reaches about 20% HP. Use Anima to hold the next boss if needed and Poison Potions to blunt Shadow Spread sleep. Completion awards Light of Vahzl and returns you to Beaucedine Glacier.",
