    source_url = "https://www.bg-wiki.com/ffxi/Promathia_Mission_6-4",
    steps = {{
    instruction = "Prep hard before One to be Feared: Reraise Hairpin or Reraise Gorget, Potions/Ethers, Echo Drops, Antidotes, Remedies for close-range jobs, HP/MP drinks, Icarus Wings for melee, normal food, and several CCB Polymer Pumps. CCB Polymer Pump comes from the Chips quest or Auction House and makes Omega and Ultima helpless for about 30 seconds. Then speak with Cid in the Metalworks at (H-8) for the cutscene.",
