  }, {
    instruction = "When everyone has watched the cutscenes, click the Iron Gate and enter the battlefield One to be Feared. Buffs wear on entry, so buff inside. The battlefield has a 45-minute limit. On the airship deck, buff quickly and click the door only when everyone is ready; one click moves the entire party into the fight.",
