    steps = {{
    instruction = "From The Garden of Ru'Hmet Home Point #1, pass through the Cermet Portal to the main elevator and choose to descend into Empyreal Paradox. Check the Transcendental Radiance for a cutscene, then check it again to enter the Dawn battleground.",
