    zone_id = 36,
  }, {
    instruction = "Defeat Promathia. Prishe and Selh'teus join the fight; Prishe can be healed or Raised, but if Selh'teus is KO'd the battle immediately fails. Promathia has two forms; after the first form you can rest before engaging the second. Watch for Seal of Quiescence mute, Winds of Oblivion amnesia, Meteor, physical/magic shields, and Nullifying Dropkick from Prishe breaking those shields.",
