    step_kind = "inspect",
    zone_id = 244,
  }, {
    instruction = "Finish the story: check the Walnut Door in Tavnazian Safehold at (K-7), then go to Lufaise Meadows and approach Blueblade Fell at (J-6), just after the first barrel on the ground, for the final cutscene. Afterward, Storms of Fate and Requiem of Sin can begin.",
