    step_kind = "inspect",
    zone_id = 24,
  }, {
    instruction = "Optional Trust windows: after defeating Promathia, examine the Dilapidated Gate in Misareaux Coast (I-11) for Trust: Ulmia before epilogue quest progress can block it. After finishing all final cutscenes, examine the Walnut Door in Tavnazian Safehold (K-7) for Prishe Trust. Further progress into Storms of Fate, Shadows of the Departed, or Apocalypse Nigh can prevent these cutscenes.",
