    instruction = "Speak to Aldo in Lower Jeuno, in the back of the Neptune's Spire Tenshodo H.Q. for a cutscene and the Silver bell.",
    map_grid = "J-8",
    notes = {"If you already have Silver bell from another nation's Magicite mission, still speak with Aldo for this nation's cutscene.", "If you still need Tenshodo access, obtain a Tenshodo Member's Card through Tenshodo Membership or buy a Tenshodo Invite from the Auction House under Others > Misc and trade it to Ghebi Damomohe inside Neptune's Spire in Lower Jeuno.", "If you are on Chains of Promathia mission A Vessel Without a Captain, that scene can appear first; talk to Aldo twice after that cutscene to trigger this mission's cutscene.", "If you have done this mission in another Nation then you already have the bell, but you still need to talk to him for a cutscene."},
