    notes = {"Optional: Talk to Sedal-Godjal again.", "When the refinrocements arrive from San d'Oria, I'll return to Windurst. The professor mustaru have forgotten about Mojiji by now. Huh? He's still getting letters. But, I'm not writing them anymore!"},
