    map_grid = "",
    notes = {"(Optional) Return to Shantotto for dialogue regarding the Glove of perpetual twilight.", "Ohohohoho! It looks like my glove of perpetual twilight had the desired effect! Ajido-Marujido's failure tor egain consciousness is the only slight complication I was able to detect... But you don't need to go and start worrying. Why, it would take mor than that to finish of fa mage that had survived my tutelage and training!...Now, about the glove of perpetual twilight. Due to a slight miscalculation on my part, the rings have become fused to the glove, I see. But don't worry. With a few twists, I'll soon have them free. I'll just hold on to the ministry rings for a little while longer. Ohohoho!", "(Optional) Return to Tosuka-Porika to report about the Book of the Gods as promised.", "Where have you been? Did Ajido-Marujido get the book open!?...Hrmm, he's fallen into a coma, has he...? He must've been drawn into the \"World of the Book.\" If he manages to return to consciousness, he will have all the knowledge contained within the Book of the Gods....If he makes it back, that is."},
